<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个星期过去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，毛克利爬上了拉玛的背。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拉玛是水牛群中最大的公牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别的动物开始跟着拉玛走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天你们自己放牛吧。”毛克利对其他孩子们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要和水牛呆在一起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利把水牛带到平原边上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是河流从森林中流出来的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他从拉玛的背上跳下来，向竹林跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>正如毛克利期待的那样，格瑞布拉德在那儿等着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们高兴地拥抱在一起，但格瑞布拉德看起来很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎回到森林里等着你呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里几乎没有食物，所以他离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很快就会回来的，毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次他会杀了你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老虎回来的时候，你在开花的树附近的峡谷等我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利指着平原对面的一块岩石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在那之前，你坐在那块石头上，好让我可以看见你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天毛克利都放水牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>日复一日，他看着格瑞布拉德坐在平原对面的岩石上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大多数的时候，毛克利只是躺在草地上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>按照狼爸爸教他的方式仔细听声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果谢尔坎走近，毛克利就一定会在寂静中听见他的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，毛克利看了一眼岩石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里是空的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他连忙把水牛赶到开着金红色花的树那边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德坐在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他背上的每根毛都竖起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎已经藏了一个月了。”格瑞布拉德说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但昨晚他和塔巴其一起穿过了平原。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“塔巴其？”毛克利不怕谢尔坎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，塔巴其是另一回事。那只豺狼非常狡猾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我在黎明时遇见塔巴其，处理掉他了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德舔了舔嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，他告诉了我一些重要的信息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎计划今晚在村口等你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎现在在哪儿？”毛克利问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在干涸的大峡谷里。河边那个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他今天打猎了吗？”毛克利问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>答案可能意味着他自己的生死。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他黎明时吃了一顿大餐。”格瑞布拉德回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。”毛克利一边思考一边大声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这意味着因为吃得很饱，他没法跑得很快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我们数量有更多，就可以攻击他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但这些水牛不会攻击他的，除非他们闻到他的气味。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我还不能用他们的语言向他们解释事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你觉得我们能弄来老虎的气味吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样的话，水牛就能闻到了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎在河里行走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样是不会留下气味的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定是塔巴其告诉他那样做的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谢尔坎自己是想不到的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利站在那里，手指放在嘴里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以带水牛穿过森林到达峡谷的尽头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们可以堵住那一端。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，谢尔坎会从另一条路逃出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们也必须堵住另一端。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利看着狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能带一半的动物去那么做吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一个人做不到，不过，我带来了一个聪明的助手。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德跑开了，跳进一个洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几秒钟后，一个灰色的脑袋突然出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>热空气中充满了熟悉的打猎嚎叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利高兴地拍起手。“阿克拉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>